Source: indi-duino
Section: science
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Jasem Mutlaq <mutlaqja@ikarustech.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 6), cdbs, cmake, libindi-dev, zlib1g-dev, libusb-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.1

Package: indi-duino
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libindi1
Description: INDI Arduino driver.
 .
 This driver enables utilizing Arduino boards as general propouse I/O. This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.

Package: indi-duino-dbg
Priority: extra
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Depends: indi-duino (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: INDI Arduino Driver.
 .
 This driver enables utilizing Arduino boards as general propouse I/O.
 This package contains the debug symbols for the this driver, useful to investigate problems in INDI.
